Written to `duckexperiments/results/claude_thinking/C02/critique_revised.md`.

**What changed from critique_initial:**
- Added explicit logging fields (session occurred, self-resolved, escalation timestamp) with engineer as owner — addresses "who records" gap
- Reframed measurement as "observational only" with explicit caveat against baseline comparison — fixes the causal-framing false certainty
- Replaced "unanimity" failure criterion with a concrete `>50%` survey threshold — removes the overweighted absolute signal
